OL,3,COnline test could speed up ADHD
OL,4,Cdiagnosis for children
OL,6,FAn online test which could help
OL,7,Fdiagnose children and young people
OL,8,Fwith Attention Deficit Hyperactivity
OL,9,FDisorder (ADHD) faster has been
OL,10,Frecommended for use on the NHS.
OL,12,FKnown as the QbTest, the computer-
OL,13,Fbased assessment tracks the movements
OL,14,Fof patients while measuring the three
OL,15,Fmain symptoms of ADHD, which are
OL,16,Finattention, impulsivity, and
OL,17,Fhyperactivity.
OL,19,FResults are then compared with
OL,20,Fpatients of the same age who do not
OL,21,Fhave ADHD.
