OL,3,COnline test could speed up ADHD
OL,4,Cdiagnosis for children
OL,6,FIn draft guidance, the National
OL,7,FInstitute for Health and Care
OL,8,FExcellence (Nice) has recommended
OL,9,FQbTest be used by the NHS to aid the
OL,10,Fdiagnosis of patients aged six to 17
OL,11,Falongside standard clinical assessment.
OL,13,FEvidence from trials suggests it could
OL,14,Fincrease the number of young patients
OL,15,Fbeing diagnosed, or having the
OL,16,Fcondition ruled out, within six months.
OL,18,FAt the moment, children and young
OL,19,Fpeople suspected of having ADHD have
OL,20,Fthe condition diagnosed or ruled out
OL,21,Ffollowing a detailed assessment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
