OL,3,COnline test could speed up ADHD
OL,4,Cdiagnosis for children
OL,6,FThis can include interviews with the
OL,7,Fchild, their parents or teachers, as
OL,8,Fwell as a physical examination to rule
OL,9,Fout other possible causes for the
OL,10,Fsymptoms.
OL,12,FMark Chapman, director of Nice's
OL,13,FHealthTech programme, said: "Evidence
OL,14,Fpresented to our committee showed the
OL,15,FQbTest could increase the number of
OL,16,Fchildren and young people who get a
OL,17,Fdiagnostic decision within six months
OL,18,Fof starting assessment."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
