OL,3,COnline test could speed up ADHD
OL,4,Cdiagnosis for children
OL,6,FThere is currently no national data
OL,7,Fpublished on referrals or waiting
OL,8,Ftimes for ADHD assessments.
OL,10,FHowever, an online survey by the
OL,11,FPetitions Committee, carried out in
OL,12,F2022, asked people for their view of
OL,13,Fassessment waiting times for ADHD and
OL,14,Fautism, and attracted 7,340 responses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
