OL,3,COnline test could speed up ADHD
OL,4,Cdiagnosis for children
OL,6,FThe research found that, among
OL,7,Fpatients who had had an ADHD
OL,8,Fdiagnosis, some 27% waited between six
OL,9,Fmonths and one year for an NHS
OL,10,Fassessment, with the same proportion
OL,11,Fwaiting between one and two years and
OL,12,F14% waiting for two to three years.
OL,14,FMr Chapman said: "Children and young
OL,15,Fpeople with ADHD deserve to receive a
OL,16,Fdiagnosis in a timely manner.
OL,18,F"We heard from our patient experts
OL,19,Fthere are challenges with current
OL,20,Fpathways.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
