OL,3,COnline test could speed up ADHD
OL,4,Cdiagnosis for children
OL,6,F"We're committed to ensuring we get
OL,7,Fthe best care to people fast while
OL,8,Fproviding value for money to the
OL,9,Ftaxpayer. This technology has the
OL,10,Fpotential to generate tangible
OL,11,Fbenefits to the lives of those waiting
OL,12,Ffor an ADHD diagnosis."
OL,14,FA consultation on the draft guidance
OL,15,Fis now under way.
OL,17,FNice was unable to make a
OL,18,Frecommendation on the use of the test
OL,19,Fto help diagnose adults suspected of
OL,20,Fhaving ADHD due to limited evidence.
